Class SharingObjectPool<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spf4j.recyclable.impl.SharingObjectPool<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BlockingDisposable, Disposable, NonValidatingRecyclingSupplier<T>, RecyclingSupplier<T>

    public final class SharingObjectPool<T>
extends Object
implements RecyclingSupplier<T>
    a object sharing pool. this pool allows for non exclusive object sharing. will always return the least shared object. TODO: synchronization is too coarse, can be improved.
    Author:
    zoly
